SUMMARY:Bones and All | Staff Selects
DESCRIPTION:After her father grows tired and disappears one day\, Maren\,
  a teenage cannibal\, goes on a journey of self-discovery across America 
 to find her mother and get an understanding of who she truly is. On this 
 journey\, she meets others just like her\, good and bad. This doomed cann
 ibalistic love story is displayed through the acting of Taylor Russell an
 d TimothĂ©e Chalamet as the main characters\, along with Mark Rylance\, A
 ndrĂ© Holland\, and ChloĂ« Sevigny. [130 min\; drama\; English]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  After her father grows tired and disapp
 ears one day\, Maren\, a teenage cannibal\, goes on a journey of self-dis
 covery across America to find her mother and get an understanding of who 
 she truly is. On this journey\, she meets others just like her\, good and
  bad. This doomed cannibalistic love story is displayed through the actin
 g of Taylor Russell and TimothĂ©e Chalamet as the main characters\, along
  with Mark Rylance\, AndrĂ© Holland\, and ChloĂ« Sevigny. [130 min\; dram
 a\; English]</p>
